# Components Structure

This project uses a combination of custom components and shadcn/ui components for the user interface.

## Core Chat Components

- [components/chat.tsx](mdc:components/chat.tsx) - Main chat interface component
- [components/message.tsx](mdc:components/message.tsx) - Individual message component
- [components/messages.tsx](mdc:components/messages.tsx) - Container for all messages
- [components/chat-header.tsx](mdc:components/chat-header.tsx) - Header for the chat interface
- [components/multimodal-input.tsx](mdc:components/multimodal-input.tsx) - Input component that handles text and file uploads

## Artifact Components

Artifacts are different types of content that can be displayed in the chat:

- [components/artifact.tsx](mdc:components/artifact.tsx) - Base artifact component
- [components/code-editor.tsx](mdc:components/code-editor.tsx) - Code editor artifact
- [components/text-editor.tsx](mdc:components/text-editor.tsx) - Text editor artifact
- [components/image-editor.tsx](mdc:components/image-editor.tsx) - Image editor artifact
- [components/sheet-editor.tsx](mdc:components/sheet-editor.tsx) - Spreadsheet editor artifact

## UI Components

- [components/ui/](mdc:components/ui) - shadcn/ui components for building the interface
- [components/markdown.tsx](mdc:components/markdown.tsx) - Markdown rendering component
- [components/theme-provider.tsx](mdc:components/theme-provider.tsx) - Theme provider for light/dark mode
